<br />\n然後早餐時段極忙<br />\n想放工阿？唔得喎，要頂早更班人食完野先得。<br />\n好！鬼叫你窮！<br />\n十一點轉更。<br />\n想放工阿？唔得喎，要頂埋午更班人食野。<br />\n我屌阿？早更班人死架？<br />\n然後一點收工。<br />\n返屋企沖涼訓教，訓醒再返。<br />\n<br />\n當時32.5/H<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2ed564a7b2570d5f7de2efc989ac88966b1ca5","tid":228340,"uid":103172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:45:51.000Z","msg":"身邊同事咩類型嘅人多"},{"pid":"69eb125f49ae9b6a5cf3e9c449ec14bf83cc196a","tid":228340,"uid":4849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"可唔可以幫朋友簽幾盒雞翼？"},{"pid":"73f7cdd335a19a4f76cfd1711700db9105e248c0","tid":228340,"uid":58393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T05:02:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做過幾個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日做&gt;12個鐘我屌你老尾即刻遞信</blockquote><br />\n咁計時薪 你返得多 人工都會<span style=\"color: red;\">多</span>d啦</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n俾人迫架！<br />\n返夜晚十點，十一點到三點都忙撚到HIHI<br />\n四點完轉更後，食野先有得透氣。<br />\n然後早餐時段極忙<br />\n想放工阿？唔得喎，要頂早更班人食完野先得。<br />\n好！鬼叫你窮！<br />\n十一點轉更。<br />\n想放工阿？唔得喎，要頂埋午更班人食野。<br />\n我屌阿？早更班人死架？<br />\n然後一點收工。<br />\n返屋企沖涼訓教，訓醒再返。<br />\n<br />\n當時32.5/H<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a0efbd9d212732575245c63c04778ff4d84820","tid":228340,"uid":58393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T05:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身邊同事咩類型嘅人多</blockquote><br />\n弱智 殘疾"},{"pid":"51654ff7728e5794deb1eb0938760b9086e31623","tid":228340,"uid":58393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T05:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以幫朋友簽幾盒雞翼？</blockquote><br />\n比折都okay既<br />\n幾盒就難請d"},{"pid":"bb36dec3d5858995da78c9df009c2c1f39870983","tid":228340,"uid":10